in.</p> <p>Installation &amp; License</p> <p>Configuration</p> <p>Scenarios of use</p>"},{"location":"bundleDiscount/version-history/","title":"Overview","text":"<p>Version history This page contains version history information about plug-in. You can directly go to a version history details by clicking on a version link from below versions.</p> <p>Version 1.0.0</p> <p>Version 1.0.1</p> <p>Version 1.1.0</p> <p>Version 1.2.0</p> <p>Version 1.1.3</p> <p>Version 1.2.1</p> <p>Version 1.2.2</p> <p>Version 1.3.0</p> <p>Version 1.3.1</p> <p>Version 1.3.2</p> <p>Version 1.3.3</p> <p>Version 1.4.0</p>"},{"location":"bundleDiscount/Version%20history/1.0.0/","title":"1.0.0","text":""},{"location":"bundleDiscount/Version%20history/1.0.0/#100","title":"1.0.0","text":"<p>!!! info \"Version Details\"     | Release Date | January 24, 2017 |     |------------------|------------------|     | Plug-In Version | 1.0.0 |     | Supported nopCommerce Version | 3.80 |</p> <p>Features:</p> <ul> <li>Create bundles with discount on base product and add product(s) to them.  </li> <li>Display active bundles to customers on product details page.  </li> <li>Add bundle to cart more than once.  </li> <li>Configure attributes for products of the bundle before adding them to cart.  </li> <li>Multi-currency support.  </li> <li>Multi-store support.</li> </ul>"},{"location":"displayReward/","title":"Overview","text":"<p>The Display Reward Points Plugin provides functionality for displaying reward points on product detail page that the customer will gain on buying the product. You can change location of displaying reward points via changing CSS selector and you can also change content and design of displaying reward points from plug-in configure page. </p> <p>Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/1.0.0/","title":"Version 1.0.0","text":""},{"location":"displayReward/1.0.0/#100","title":"1.0.0","text":"Release Date March 19, 2017 Plug-In Version 1.0.0 Supported nopCommerce Version 3.80"},{"location":"displayReward/1.0.0/#features","title":"Features","text":"<ol> <li>Display reward point on product detail page.  </li> <li>Customizable CSS selector for the display reward point.  </li> <li>Customizable content and design of display reward point.  </li> <li>Multi-store Supported.  </li> </ol> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/1.0.1/","title":"1.0.1","text":"Release Date March 19, 2017 Plug-In Version 1.0.1 Supported nopCommerce Version 3.80"},{"location":"displayReward/1.0.1/#features","title":"Features","text":"<ol> <li>Update user manual.  </li> <li>Added help document link in plug-in configure page.</li> </ol> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/1.1.0/","title":"1.1.0","text":"Release Date March 28, 2017 Plug-In Version 1.1.0 Supported nopCommerce Version 3.90"},{"location":"displayReward/1.1.0/#features","title":"Features","text":"<ul> <li>Upgraded to nopCommerce 3.90</li> </ul> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/1.2.0/","title":"1.2.0","text":"Release Date February 01, 2018 Plug-In Version 1.2.0 Supported nopCommerce Version 4.00"},{"location":"displayReward/1.2.0/#features","title":"Features","text":"<ul> <li>Upgraded to nopCommerce 4.00</li> </ul> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/1.3.0/","title":"1.3.0","text":"Release Date September 05, 2018 Plug-In Version 1.3.0 Supported nopCommerce Version 4.10"},{"location":"displayReward/1.3.0/#features","title":"Features","text":"<ul> <li>Added support for nopCommerce 4.10  </li> <li>Added Multi-Language support in 4.10  </li> </ul>"},{"location":"displayReward/1.3.0/#bug-fix","title":"Bug Fix","text":"<ul> <li>Reward points calculation fixed for grouped products in 4.10</li> </ul> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/49.0.0/","title":"49.0.0","text":"Release Date October 28, 2025 Plug-In Version 49.0.0 Supported nopCommerce Version 4.90"},{"location":"displayReward/49.0.0/#features","title":"Features","text":"<ul> <li>Upgraded to nopCommerce 4.90 </li> </ul> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/Configuration/","title":"Configuration","text":""},{"location":"displayReward/Configuration/#general-tab-configuration","title":"General Tab Configuration","text":"<p>This plug-in displays reward points on the product detail page that a customer would earn based on the product amount and the configured reward point settings.</p> <p>\u26a0\ufe0f Note: The plug-in will not work if reward points settings are disabled in nopCommerce. To enable reward point settings, go to: Configuration \u2192 Settings \u2192 Reward Points and enable it along with other reward point configurations.</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/Configuration/#display-configuration","title":"Display Configuration","text":"<ul> <li> <p>You can choose where to display reward points for the product amount using \"CSS selector for Reward points\".   Reward points will appear after the element defined by your selector.</p> </li> <li> <p>You can customize the HTML content with inline CSS styles in the \"Display content\" text box as per your preference.</p> </li> </ul> <p>\ud83d\udca1 Important: It is mandatory to include the keyword <code>RewardPoints</code> in your text where you want the calculated reward points to appear. Without <code>RewardPoints</code>, only static text will be displayed on the product details page (no reward points will be shown).</p> <p></p> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/Feature/","title":"Features","text":"<ul> <li>Display reward points on product detail page</li> <li>Display reward points on Grouped product detail page</li> <li>Automatically calculates reward points for products as per configuration of reward point</li> <li>Customizable CSS selector for the display reward points</li> <li>Customizable content and design of display reward points</li> <li>Multi-store Supported, Multi-Language Supported(nopCommerce-4.10), Supported version(s) </li> </ul> <p>Supported Version(s): 3.80, 3.90, 4.00, 4.10, 4.20, 4.30, 4.40, 4.50, 4.60 , 4.70, 4.80 and 4.90</p> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/Help/","title":"How to Get Help","text":"<p>If you face any issues, you can:</p> <ul> <li>Email us at support@nopaccelerate.com</li> <li>Or use the support form: http://www.nopaccelerate.com/wiki/support</li> </ul> <p>You can also send us the exact steps to reproduce the issue by recording it using the Problem Steps Recorder (psr.exe) on Windows:</p> <ol> <li>Open Run in Windows and type <code>psr.exe</code>, then press Enter.</li> <li>Click Start Record and perform the steps that produce the issue.</li> <li>When done, click Stop Record.</li> <li>You will be prompted to save a .zip file.</li> <li>Email the saved .zip file to us along with a short description of the issue.</li> </ol> <p></p> <p>\u2190 Previous </p>"},{"location":"displayReward/History/","title":"Version History","text":"<p>This page contains version history information about plug-in. You can directly go to a version history details by clicking on a version link from below versions.</p> <p>Version 49.0.0</p> <p>Version 1.0.0</p> <p>Version 1.0.1</p> <p>Version 1.1.0</p> <p>Version 1.2.0</p> <p>Version 1.3.0</p> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/Licence/","title":"Installation &amp; Licensing","text":"<p>Download the plug-in object code and place it in your Plugins folder, then follow the standard nopCommerce plug-in installation procedure.</p> <p>The Display Reward Points plug-in appears under the Promotions group on the Local plugins page.</p> <p>Once installed:</p> <ol> <li>Go to your nopCommerce Admin Panel.</li> <li>Navigate to: Configuration \u2192 Plugins \u2192 Local plugins \u2192 Display Reward Points plugin</li> <li>The plug-in will prompt you to enter your license key (as shown in the figure below).</li> <li>Enter the license key you received via email after purchasing the plug-in from our website.</li> </ol> <p></p> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/senerioOfUse/","title":"Scenerios of Use","text":"<p>This section provides common usage scenarios for the Display Reward Points plug-in.</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/senerioOfUse/#product-detail-page","title":"Product Detail Page","text":"<p>Reward points are displayed on the product detail page.</p> <p> </p> <p>\u2190 Previous | Next \u2192</p>"},{"location":"displayReward/sub-child1/","title":"Sub child1","text":"<p>This sub child</p>"}]}
